{"title":"为巴黎和平大会作","authors":["马凡陀"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":4,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为巴黎和平大会作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马凡陀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野心家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野心家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野心大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制造原子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积极练兵马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想把世界吞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想把战争打。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野心家是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国资本家！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国招兵要打仗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经济恐慌货难销，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"货色堆得山样高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工厂停工又减产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失业工人八百万。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失业多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么办！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"救济所门口立个招兵站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰、杰克，请进来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱去你身上的工人装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿起免费的卡其衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一枝冲锋枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几百毒气弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去打各地的“叛国者”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去打“肮脏”的苏维埃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁威胁我国的领土、安全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们就打谁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的领土在希腊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的国界在挪威，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的前线在菲洲阿尔及尔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一直到扬子江、台湾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的贫农分得了一亩地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜的孩子认识了三个字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东欧的工人多吃了一块面包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的安全就失去了保障！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么地方人民不饿死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么地方人民不上吊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么地方老太太也投票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国式的民主就危险了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当兵好，当兵好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愁失业不愁病，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活问题解决了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"退伍兵政府管养老。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰，请！杰克，来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送你吃，送你穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送你世界各地去玩花姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国世纪万万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（新华社北平二十七日电）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}